  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "After running the `create-release-branch` script, the commit message matches the pattern `Release <version>` with the branch following `Release/<version>`. If you use squash on a release PR on github, the commit message becomes the branch name, causes the release to be skipped.\r\n\r\nTo fix this issue, the release script should allow both patterns.",
